[1] Cases around the world
Date: Fri 27 May 2022
Source: Reuters [edited]
https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/monkeypox-cases-around-world-2022-05-23/


Below is a list of countries that have so far reported suspected or confirmed cases, in alphabetical order. [Note: All cases in 2022, reported case numbers have increased in some of the countries listed below since this list was published. - Mod.TY]

Asia-Pacific
* Australia on [20 May 2022] reported its 1st case in a traveller who recently returned from Britain. Another suspected case was also identified.

Europe
* Austria confirmed its 1st case on [22 May 2022].
* Belgium detected 2 cases on [20 May 2022].
* Czech Republic detected its 1st case on [24 May 2022].
* Denmark confirmed a 2nd case on [24 May 2022], a day after the 1st.
* Finland confirmed its 1st case on [27 May 2022].
* France's number of confirmed cases rose to 5 on [25 May 2022].
* Germany has confirmed 3 cases, with the 1st registered on [20 May 2022].
* Italy has confirmed 9 cases by [26 May 2022]. It detected its 1st case on [19 May 2022].
* The Netherlands reported its 1st case on [20 May 2022]. It has since confirmed "several" more patients, without stating the exact number.
* Portugal confirmed 16 new cases on [27 May 2022], bringing the total to 74.
* Slovenia confirmed its 1st case on [24 May 2022].
* Spain confirmed 25 new cases on [26 May 2022], bringing the total to 84.
* Sweden confirmed its 1st case on [19 May 2022].
* Switzerland reported its 1st confirmed case on [21 May 2022].
* The UK detected 14 new cases in England on [24 May 2022], taking the total of identified cases to 70.

Middle East
* Israel confirmed its 1st case on [21 May 2022].
* The UAE detected its 1st case on [24 May 2022], state news agency WAM reported.

Americas
* Argentina reported its 1st suspected case on [23 May 2022].
* Canada reported 10 new infections on [27 May 2022], bringing its total to 25.
* USA confirmed 9 additional cases in 7 states on [26 May 2022]. The total number of infections is up at 11 since the 1st infection was discovered on [18 May 2022].

